  <p class="why-intro">Every year, <strong>100,000 students</strong> compete for fewer than <strong>5,000 roles</strong>. Most fail before they ever get an interview — not because they aren't smart enough, but because nobody told them what they were doing wrong.</p>
  <div class="why-grid">
