    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-stat">5,000</div><div class="why-card-title">Graduate roles. 100,000 applicants.</div><div class="why-card-desc">100,000 students. 5,000 roles. Students who get through are better prepared and know what the interviewer is actually looking for.</div></div>
