    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-stat">11<em>pm</em></div><div class="why-card-title">When most students start preparing</div><div class="why-card-desc">The night before a deadline. The Desk is the 7:30am daily briefing that means you're never starting from zero.</div></div>
    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-stat">£0</div><div class="why-card-title">What most students spend on proper prep</div><div class="why-card-desc">They rely on forums and outdated prep books. Students who invest in real preparation convert at a completely different rate.</div></div>
    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-stat">1</div><div class="why-card-title">You only get one go at applying</div><div class="why-card-desc">Don't waste it. Most students show up under-prepared and find out too late. The Desk gets you ready before applications open — not after they close.</div></div>
